  "description": [
    "AYERS CHERRY PECTORAL FOR THE CURE OF COUGHS COLDS INFLUENZA HOARSENESS CROUP BRONCHITIS INCIPIENT CONSUMPTION AND FOR THE RELIEF OF CONSUMPTIVE PATIENTS IN ADVANCED STAGES OF THE DISEASE It is the best preparation of wild cherry known and has been more successful in the cure of Pulmonary Diseases than any other medicine ever discovered FOB COUGHS AND COLDS it i truly an invaluable Remedy often curing the most obstinate cases with surprising rapidity and thus saving the health and lives of thousands a year Witness the following certificate Dr James C Ayer Lowell Dear Sir Feel ing under obligations to you for the restoration of my health I send you this report of my cose which you are at liberty to publish for the benefit of others in distress During the autumn I took a bad cold accompa nied by a severe cough and no medicine I could procure would relievo me I could not sleep nights or work days until by the advice of a friend I pro cured a bottle of your Cherry Pectoral which im mediately helped and in a few days cured me Respectfully JAMES J CHILDNESS Corner Ninth and Vino Streets Philadelphia AS A FAMILY"
  ],
